Name: Crash Rickshaw
rawData: Crash Rickshaw is a side project of the post-hardcore band Project 86. It was founded by Alex Albert, Steven Dail and Joby Harris, with Randy Torres joining later. Crash Rickshaw released their self-titled album on September 11, 2001 on Tooth & Nail Records. Their second album, The Unknown Clarity, was released on iTunes on March 11, 2008.
